{"tid":386054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣屋企人做過嘅感動野","createTime":"2017-09-03T15:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T14:01:04.000Z","uid":4375,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f19d3dca2b0f3a84e902002742d8847eab5630a","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"幾年前我要出國讀書，有次我係屋企訓緊教，媽咪突發入左嚟我間房跟住摸我塊面，係到講：Jean, 媽咪好唔捨得你啊，你就嚟去外國啦，媽咪真係好唔捨得你好唔捨得你<br />\n跟住佢見我醒醒地，佢就話：你起身就要去買衫買去外面嘅野啦，訓醒打比媽咪啦<br />\n佢出左去之後我喊爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32ddd8fac36c9fd3088586ab92a0860963e19b4","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"你地都分享啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c20cf0cb093fe3f09b95da8b9a135988e69bd3","tid":386054,"uid":79709,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母煮左暗黑理料出黎 <br />\n難食到嘔，老豆拍我肩頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：啊仔你唔好再食啦，等我黎啦<br />\n個一刻覺得老豆真係好型 好man"},{"pid":"fec97b86340eeb67197c63204226c78a812a774a","tid":386054,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"一畢業送左部車比我做禮物"},{"pid":"0d232daf237a83fadd75cd6658e6ece944656527","tid":386054,"uid":83495,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"細個老豆打2份工 晚晚2 3點先返 仲唔訓住煮意粉俾我同家姐食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9284ddcbd009e7963fa3996ea66e35c059234b","tid":386054,"uid":137417,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"同個ex分手之後一個禮拜,終於有日忍唔住喺阿爸阿媽面前爆喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地一直都喺我身邊陪住我,阿媽更加係擔心我搞到訓得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢次之後始於明白父母既愛,佢地有幾愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家打算紋佢地個名,等我呢一世都唔好忘記佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f1febead71f03ce03145b8e5ea619e1e7de189","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母煮左暗黑理料出黎 <br />\n難食到嘔，老豆拍我肩頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：啊仔你唔好再食啦，等我黎啦<br />\n個一刻覺得老豆真係好型 好man</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13857f3af82968a8e7e0cf0ac8e475ccfc648276","tid":386054,"uid":11229,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母煮左暗黑理料出黎 <br />\n難食到嘔，老豆拍我肩頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：啊仔你唔好再食啦，等我黎啦<br />\n個一刻覺得老豆真係好型 好man</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老豆真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n但你用既公仔有咩意思？"},{"pid":"3b6e806c3c941714b9f8cd90db82e9f731508601","tid":386054,"uid":82542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"You win 睇到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b05012208d13e288957c0482ef1b4b801be2ca2","tid":386054,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前我要出國讀書，有次我係屋企訓緊教，媽咪突發入左嚟我間房跟住摸我塊面，係到講：Jean, 媽咪好唔捨得你啊，你就嚟去外國啦，媽咪真係好唔捨得你好唔捨得你<br />\n跟住佢見我醒醒地，佢就話：你起身就要去買衫買去外面嘅野啦，訓醒打比媽咪啦<br />\n佢出左去之後我喊爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你即刻起身，攬住佢，一切喊，會係個完美的畫面"},{"pid":"e5675f4d2d40ed1ff0d799731a4a01aaa3bfb980","tid":386054,"uid":143383,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"之前我隻狗出左意外<br />\n嗰陣我翻緊學<br />\n得我爸喺屋企<br />\n我爸就帶左隻狗出街<br />\n之後可能分心睇其他野<br />\n隻狗比另一隻狗咬到好傷<br />\n我放學翻到去喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊送去醫院邊責怪我爸<br />\n一直鬧佢，佢都冇出聲<br />\n最後我狗做手術兼留醫幾日<br />\n我喊到翻屋企，入翻房<br />\n佢冇啦啦走左入黎<br />\n跪喺地下同我講：對唔住呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要怪就怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻拉翻佢起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個男人除左求婚仲點會有其他情況跪喺地下<br />\n何況嗰個係我爸<br />\n最後當然我都有同我爸道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個前世情人真係好錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲肯放低尊嚴跪喺度同我道歉"},{"pid":"9542a27cb0f7c98ba9ed6653f440f3703df04611","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年前我要出國讀書，有次我係屋企訓緊教，媽咪突發入左嚟我間房跟住摸我塊面，係到講：Jean, 媽咪好唔捨得你啊，你就嚟去外國啦，媽咪真係好唔捨得你好唔捨得你<br />\n跟住佢見我醒醒地，佢就話：你起身就要去買衫買去外面嘅野啦，訓醒打比媽咪啦<br />\n佢出左去之後我喊爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你即刻起身，攬住佢，一切喊，會係個完美的畫面</blockquote><br />\n我唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我係個好收埋自己情緒嘅人"},{"pid":"47210e0bc2c3b891659ebd7a3d5c77de7cd0efb8","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>You win 睇到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我咁大個人都係痴住媽咪，佢去邊我都去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以感情真係好好"},{"pid":"dd5c0668809fa8788dd44bc808d68a5d093f5360","tid":386054,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"分享下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d6a5b8e16d1d553b21407a3eb1508cba56a144","tid":386054,"uid":106506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"屋企人用緊廁所 我突然急屎想開大<br />\n佢9秒9出黎 比我屙左先"},{"pid":"2cf8069a2057c0bfdc1db180f836f56f44076b43","tid":386054,"uid":136618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母煮左暗黑理料出黎 <br />\n難食到嘔，老豆拍我肩頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：啊仔你唔好再食啦，等我黎啦<br />\n個一刻覺得老豆真係好型 好man</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你是咪有兩個老豆"},{"pid":"1327890af222d09195b2d30ea08c41105d0c8a6c","tid":386054,"uid":136618,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"初中完全唔撚讀書，跌出全級100名外，後來高中先開始覺得有責任要照顧屋企，急起直追。<br />\n<br />\n考完DSE淨返bio未考，數學係core最後一科，自問都放咗好多時間落去溫，點知都係覺得失晒手考得好差，嗰晚喊晒好唔開心，喊得仲犀利過放榜嗰日，我媽攬住我：「唔緊要㗎，我知我個仔已經好叻，媽媽睇到㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n其實你個仔一啲都唔叻，最叻就係投胎搵啱個好人家，做到你個仔，有你同你老公養到我咁大；爸爸仲要係老師，讀撚到Master，但從來都無畀壓力我，放榜嗰日都係話：「你都係唔輸得先努力咗咁耐，咁我就同你一齊行到最尾睇吓你會唔會叻過我贏到我！」<br />\n<br />\n放榜，數學都有4，見得吓人啦，不過predict考得好嘅卷有啲好有啲就失手，中文分卷有攞level2有攞5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排就開sem、開學，唔知會有幾多學生睇到呢個comment，但我想你哋知讀書、放榜都只係個學習嘅過程，你要學識屋企人可能用緊一種意想不到嘅方式去支持你，<br />\n<br />\n同老一輩有咁大個代溝，同屋企人相處越嚟越難，但長輩嘅心思，係要用啲時間去接納同探索，你就會知道親情係幾咁難能可貴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c62e3aa1ec4e180886712116982fc841168e772","tid":386054,"uid":134888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:51:49.000Z","msg":"試過同老母嘈交，老母經常否認我嘅努力。由細到大，都未試過讚過我一次。但係有一次，我去老母返工地方比野佢。見到老母係佢同事面前係咁讚我，到我遇到困難時候，老母永遠都係背後支持我。<br />\n  試過鬥氣唔想屋企人幫我俾大學學費，自己返工返到死死下，第二日老母就將佢幸苦錢俾我做學費。<br />\n   雖然我老豆係廢，但係我老母真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410ab50936d773039ad297c3460aa7e2ab515f89","tid":386054,"uid":41793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我隻狗出左意外<br />\n嗰陣我翻緊學<br />\n得我爸喺屋企<br />\n我爸就帶左隻狗出街<br />\n之後可能分心睇其他野<br />\n隻狗比另一隻狗咬到好傷<br />\n我放學翻到去喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊送去醫院邊責怪我爸<br />\n一直鬧佢，佢都冇出聲<br />\n最後我狗做手術兼留醫幾日<br />\n我喊到翻屋企，入翻房<br />\n佢冇啦啦走左入黎<br />\n跪喺地下同我講：對唔住呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要怪就怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻拉翻佢起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個男人除左求婚仲點會有其他情況跪喺地下<br />\n何況嗰個係我爸<br />\n最後當然我都有同我爸道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個前世情人真係好錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲肯放低尊嚴跪喺度同我道歉</blockquote><br />\n<del><del></del></del>"},{"pid":"24cabc8bea675f696b43904cc240f6f861185b33","tid":386054,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:05:28.000Z","msg":"我屋企人無做過任何事令我感動<br />\n由細打到我大，打到我心理變態<br />\n默書80分又打，85分無飯食<br />\n90分有飯俾我食但係黑我面<br />\n唔好迫我諗以前嘅嘢屌你老母"},{"pid":"9dc97c60268638dfe20d07dc0adec0b41968b34a","tid":386054,"uid":59754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企人用緊廁所 我突然急屎想開大<br />\n佢9秒9出黎 比我屙左先</blockquote><br />\n我一樣試過，不過係仆街大佬99年都唔出黎，我暈左落我娘親度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:瀨9晒"},{"pid":"eb1c41cb2756f63fdac61b1dac09b3cb7b76658f","tid":386054,"uid":84369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:14:30.000Z","msg":"所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲肯支持我呢個仔真係好多謝佢地<br />\n但永遠唔敢講出口"},{"pid":"f11950e99ac1c9b9eee313d774041e448d045f53","tid":386054,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企人用緊廁所 我突然急屎想開大<br />\n佢9秒9出黎 比我屙左先</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母我細個得幾歲大屙緊屎<br />\n突然老豆老母拍我廁所門<br />\n叫我即刻出嚟 我未去完督屎喊住出去<br />\n原來又要打我 因咩事打我已經唔記得<br />\n淨係記得打到成地血"},{"pid":"fa05c1789fc31dd80602d7c4048a5a67d8960042","tid":386054,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:20:07.000Z","msg":"咪撚再講乜9屋企感動嘢 講果個死果個"},{"pid":"726e314ace4da7fc025b2887b1e9b729d3873a2f","tid":386054,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋企人用緊廁所 我突然急屎想開大<br />\n佢9秒9出黎 比我屙左先</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母我細個得幾歲大屙緊屎<br />\n突然老豆老母拍我廁所門<br />\n叫我即刻出嚟 我未去完督屎喊住出去<br />\n原來又要打我 因咩事打我已經唔記得<br />\n淨係記得打到成地血</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母有無睇過三五成群<br />\n我細個就好似阿雞咁<br />\n我命大死唔撚去 我依家一蚊家用都唔會俾兩個仆街"}]}